data.description: Wow now is your chance to purchase a home and get INSTANT EQUITY! Quite simply the best deal in West Bradenton. You will NOT find a LARGER HOME for this price! Located in a premier location near the hospital, GT Bray Park and close to Anna Maria Island...this is a CAN'T MISS HOME! With some simple and inexpensive cosmetic updates you can easily gain a ton of value. The roof was just replaced in 2020! Offering 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms and over 3,300 sqft of living space this amazing home is priced under $200 per sqft!!! Featuring tons of curb appeal with the tropical landscaping, siding and decorative stone facade. The interior offers loads of space and the natural light beams throughout the many windows and skylights in the home. The recently updated kitchen will have you smiling as soon as you see it!  Truly the heart of the home with new granite countertops, stainless steel appliances including a double oven and farmhouse sink, and a huge island with pendant lighting and tons of seating. The massive walk in pantry is an additional bonus.  There are two bedrooms downstairs both with ensuite bathrooms. Additional rooms include the the formal dining room, family room, living room and an office. The downstairs laundry room is directly off the oversized two car garage and serves as the perfect mud room as well. The powder room is also located in this vicinity which serves as the perfect guest bathroom. Upstairs you will find an additional bedroom and bathroom, bonus area, and the large master suite! The real magic of this home is the backyard! Truly a hidden gem with no direct neighbors behind you. Mature shaded oak tress and a large brick pavered patio will have you sitting in the backyard enjoying the serenity of the Florida lifestyle! Nestled in the tranquil Point West neighborhood offering low HOA fees. Conveniently located just minutes away from the pristine white sandy beaches of Anna Maria Island, and a short drive to vibrant downtown St. Petersburg & the rich cultural and culinary offerings of Sarasota, this property also provides easy access to the boat ramp and Robinson Preserve, a 682-acre nature preserve offering trails, kayak launches, scenic lookouts, and more. DO NOT WAIT ON THIS SPECTACULAR DEAL!
